cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper deals with automated road network extraction from remote sensing imagery using computer vision techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graph-theoretic metrics and optimization, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The use of machine learning algorithms and the high quality dataset also indicates that it could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
